=============================================

ZeferoShield .gitignore — PROTECTED FROM PUBLIC

=============================================

Environment & Secrets

.env .env.local .env..local .env credentials.json secrets.json
config/secrets/*

API Keys & Tokens

keys/ .key .pem .crt .p12 *.pfx

Commercial / Closed-source modules

src/zeferozero/ src/zeferopulse/ src/zeferovault/ src/zeferoattack/
zefero-zero/ zefero-pulse/ zefero-vault/ zefero-attack/

Hardware & Device-specific

hardware/ rpi-config/ hailo-config/ npu-firmware/ freenove-hat/
pi5-specific/ .hcl .toml.local

Build & Runtime artifacts

target/ dist/ build/ out/ node_modules/ .exe .dll .so .dylib

Logs & Temp files

logs/ .log .tmp temp/ cache/

IDE & Editor files

.vscode/ .idea/ .swp .swo .DS_Store

Local development only

docker-compose.override.yml docker-compose.local.yml local/

Test data that may contain real info

test/data/real-* test/secrets/

Patent & Internal documents (if any)

internal/ patent-drafts/ confidential/

Compiled binaries (except ZeferoX public release)

zeferox--private zeferoguard--private
